p.cl:
Witness, Andrew, archdeacon of Lothian; Walter, archdeacon of St Andrews;
                  Geoffrey, abbot of Dunfermline; John, abbot of Holyrood;
                  Amfred, abbot of Newbattle; Roger, abbot of Dryburgh; Aiulf
                  and Patrick, deans; Geoffrey of Lasswade; Robert of Perth;
                  Alexander and Albinus, chaplains; Geoffrey, clerk, of
                  Tyninghame.
